-- China's Wen to Maintain Economic Policies, Spur Local Demand, Xinhua Says
-- James Regan
-- 2010-07-18T10:11:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-18/china-s-wen-to-maintain-economic-policies-spur-local-demand-xinhua-says.html

          
          
             Chinese Premier Wen Jiabao pledged
to maintain the nation’s current economic policies to ensure
favorable conditions for businesses, the official Xinhua News
Agency reported.  
 Wen, speaking on a three-day visit to Xi’an, capital of
Shaanxi province, said the global economy is recovering at a
slow pace and China should expand domestic demand to create
jobs.  
